Resource Profile: Stroke Patient based on the Brazilian RNDS ( Experimental )

Official URL: https://molic-avc.gabriellesantosleandro.com/StructureDefinition/StrokePatient Version: 0.0.0
Active as of 2024-01-11 Computable Name: StrokePatient

This profile stores demographics and other administrative information about a patient with stroke, based on the Brazilian National Data Network (RNDS).

Demografia e outras informações administrativas de um atendimento de saúde para um paciente que sofreu AVC baseado na RNDS e na ICHOM.

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: Cardiovascular Comorbidities, Stroke Severity: Consciousness, Diagnosis Evidence Base, Discharge Destination Following Acute Care Hospitalization... Show 20 more, Estimated Stroke Severity: based on NIHSS Category, Hemicraniectomy, Prior Atrial Fibrillation and Flutter, Prior Diabetes Mellitus, Prior Hyperlipidemia, Prior Hypertension, Prior Ischemic Heart Disease, Prior Myocardial Infarction, Prior Stroke excluding Transient Ischemic Attacks, Prior Transient Ischemic Attacks, Procoagulant Reversal Therapy, Inpatient Acute Care Rehabilitation, Post Acute Care Rehabilitation, Stroke Recurrence., Stroke Severity: NIHSS Score, Stroke Type, Symptomatic Intracranial Hemorrhage, Duration of Stroke Symptoms, Thrombectomy and Thrombolytic Therapy
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Patient/example-strokepatient
